com.yahoo.document.annotation

Class AnnotationTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.document.annotation.AnnotationTypes

  • public final class AnnotationTypes
extends Object
    This is a container for all Annotations constants used by built-in Vespa features. These must be in sync with the corresponding class in the C++ file 'document/datatype/annotationtype.h'.
    Author:
    Simon Thoresen
